The paper deals with the problem of selecting a subset of agents as leaders in a multi-agent network to achieve desired performance. This problem is related to the fields of control systems (cs.SY), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), robotics (cs.RO), distributed computing (cs.DC), and machine learning (cs.LG).
